 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">When there is a cost of maternal effects, minimizing it is traded off against minimizing the phenotypic variance (eq. 
  <a rid="evo12635-disp-0010" ref-type="disp-formula" href="#evo12635-disp-0010">8c</a>). When 
  <div id="nlm-math-124" class="math">
   <div class="msub">
